column2: SELECT  SpecObj.plate, SpecObj.mjd, SpecObj.fiberID, SpecObj.z, GalSpecLine.h_alpha_flux, GalSpecLine.h_beta_flux  FROM SpecObj JOIN GalSpecLine ON  SpecObj.specobjid = GalSpecLine.specobjid WHERE  h_alpha_flux > #*h_beta_flux AND SpecObj.class = &&& AND SpecObj.z between # and #  AND SpecObj.sn1_g >#
